eign-tourists/113-tips-and-things-to-remember-before-you-go</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- <strong><span style="color: blue;">For accommodation in <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Vietnam</st1:place></st1:country-region></span></strong>, the information is available at http://www.vietnamhotels.net/</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">- <strong><span style="color: blue;">For the specific tips during your trip in <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Vietnam</st1:place></st1:country-region></span></strong>, it can be reached at:</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">http://www.vntraveltips.com/while-youre-in-vietnam</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">-<span style="">&nbsp; </span><strong><a href="http://www.vntraveltips.com/while-youre-in-vietnam/do-a-dont">DOs &amp; DON''Ts (While You are in Vietnam)</a></strong>, learn out more at http://www.vntraveltips.com/while-youre-in-vietnam/do-a-dont/68-general-dos-a-donts-for-vietnam</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">-<span style="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style="color: blue;">For the most beautiful beaches, famous attractions as well as cultural activities and most traditional food and drink</span></strong>, you can find at: http://www.vietnam-beauty.com/</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">We do hope that the above information can be helpful and wish you a happy and unforgettable trip in <st1:place w:st="on"><st1:country-region w:st="on">Vietnam</st1:country-region></st1:place>!</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Should you have any questions regarding in <st1:country-region w:st="on"><st1:place w:st="on">Vietnam</st1:place></st1:country-region>, we are always available at:</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p></o:p>Client Support:+84.4625.12.798 or hotline: +84.946.583.583.</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Email: support@vietnam-visa.com</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">We warmly welcome Mr/Ms [full name] to our beautiful country.<br style="" />\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br style="" />\r\n<!--[endif]--></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal">Visa Support Department<br />\r\nVNB Travel</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\r\n<div id="refHTML">&nbsp;</div>', 'InActive');
